      <title>Meta 的股价反弹显示了大规模裁员的回报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/meta-s-stock-bounce-shows-how-big-ticket-job-cuts-can-pay-off</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财报电话会议上提到裁员的比例是大流行以来的最高水平——正如 Meta Platforms Inc. 所表明的那样，这种成本削减可以为投资者带来回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/meta-s-stock-bounce-shows-how-big-ticket-job-cuts-can-pay-off</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 12:02:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
